column2: pendingFinalization        Number of objects that are pending finalization in the java VM.
column3: daemonThreads        Current number of live daemon threads in this VM.
column4: threads        Current number of live threads (both daemon and non-daemon) in this VM.
column5: peakThreads        High water mark of live threads in this VM.
column6: threadStarts        Total number of times a thread has been started since this vm started.
column7: cpus        Number of cpus available to the java VM on its machine.
column8: loadedClasses        Total number of classes loaded since vm started.
column9: unloadedClasses        Total number of classes unloaded since vm started.
column10: freeMemory        An approximation fo the total amount of memory currently available for future allocated objects, measured in bytes.
column11: totalMemory        The total amount of memory currently available for current and future objects, measured in bytes.
column12: maxMemory        The maximum amount of memory that the VM will attempt to use, measured in bytes.
column13: processCpuTime        CPU timed used by the process in nanoseconds.
column14: fdLimit        Maximum number of file descriptors
column15: fdsOpen        Current number of open file descriptors
